---
import { SEMINARIO, CHECKOUT_GRATUITO, CHECKOUT_VIP, CHECKOUT_PLATINUM } from '../config/seminario';
---
<section id="tiers" class="py-16 md:py-24 px-6 scroll-mt-4 relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-b from-white via-[#F5F5F5] to-white">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-25">
    <div class="absolute top-10 right-0 w-96 h-96 rounded-full bg-[#4CAF50]" style="filter: blur(120px);"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-0 w-80 h-80 rounded-full bg-[#2C3E99]" style="filter: blur(100px);"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <span class="inline-block mb-4 px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-[#2C3E99]/10 text-[#2C3E99] text-xs md:text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
        Escolha seu nível de participação
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-3">Três formas de aproveitar o Seminário</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Todas as opções incluem o Seminário ao vivo. Escolha a opção que faz mais sentido para você.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8 items-stretch">

      {/* GRATUITO */}
      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl border-2 border-gray-200 p-6 md:p-7 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow flex flex-col">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Plano Gratuito</p>
        <div class="mb-5 pb-5 border-b border-gray-100">
          <p class="text-4xl font-black text-gray-900">R$ 0</p>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1">Acesso ao Seminário ao vivo</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 mb-6 flex-1">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-[#4CAF50] font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Acesso completo</strong> ao Seminário ao vivo</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-[#4CAF50] font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Certificado de participação digital</strong> — {SEMINARIO.cargaGratuita} de formação</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href={CHECKOUT_GRATUITO} data-tier="gratuito" class="js-tier-cta block w-full text-center text-[#2C3E99] font-extrabold text-base py-4 rounded-xl border-2 border-[#2C3E99] hover:bg-[#2C3E99] hover:text-white transition-colors">
          INSCRIÇÃO GRATUITA
        </a>
      </div>

      {/* VIP */}
      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl border-2 border-[#2C3E99] p-6 md:p-7 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow flex flex-col">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold text-[#2C3E99] uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Plano VIP</p>
        <div class="mb-5 pb-5 border-b border-gray-100">
          <p class="text-4xl font-black text-[#2C3E99]">R$ 19,70</p>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1">Pagamento único</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 mb-6 flex-1">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-[#4CAF50] font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Todo o conteúdo do Plano Gratuito</strong></span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-[#4CAF50] font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Certificado Assinado no GOV.BR</strong> no formato PDF — {SEMINARIO.cargaVip} de capacitação profissional</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-[#4CAF50] font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Encontro exclusivo com a Gua</strong> — 30 minutos antes da aula para conversar e tirar dúvidas</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-[#4CAF50] font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Acesso vitalício</strong> à gravação da aula (replay)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-[#4CAF50] font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Material completo da aula</strong> em PDF para consultar quando precisar</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href={CHECKOUT_VIP} data-tier="vip" class="js-tier-cta block w-full text-center text-white font-black text-base py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-150 active:scale-[0.98]" style="background:#2C3E99; box-shadow: 0 5px 0 #1a2570;">
          QUERO SER VIP
        </a>
      </div>

      {/* PLATINUM */}
      <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-b from-[#faf5ff] via-white to-[#f5f3ff] rounded-3xl border-4 border-[#7C3AED] p-6 md:p-7 shadow-2xl flex flex-col" style="box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.35);">
        <span class="absolute -top-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#7C3AED] to-[#5B21B6] text-white text-xs md:text-sm font-black px-5 py-1.5 rounded-full shadow-lg whitespace-nowrap">
          ⭐ MAIS ESCOLHIDO
        </span>
        <p class="text-xs font-bold text-[#7C3AED] uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 mt-2">Plano Platinum</p>
        <div class="mb-5 pb-5 border-b border-purple-100">
          <p class="text-4xl font-black text-[#7C3AED]">R$ 39,70</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-1">Experiência completa</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 mb-6 flex-1">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-[#7C3AED] font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Todos os benefícios do Plano VIP</strong></span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-[#7C3AED] font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Certificado Assinado no GOV.BR</strong> no formato PDF — {SEMINARIO.cargaPlatinum} de capacitação profissional</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-[#7C3AED] font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Certificado físico impresso</strong> entregue em sua casa pelos Correios</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-[#7C3AED] font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span><strong>15 Modelos Prontos de Relatórios</strong> para usar na sua prática docente</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-[#7C3AED] font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Grupo de suporte prioritário</strong> para tirar dúvidas e networking com outras professoras</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-[#7C3AED] font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Bônus exclusivo:</strong> Aula extra gravada + Ebook especial</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href={CHECKOUT_PLATINUM} data-tier="platinum" class="js-tier-cta block w-full text-center text-white font-black text-base py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-150 active:scale-[0.98]" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7C3AED 0%, #5B21B6 100%); box-shadow: 0 5px 0 #4C1D95;">
          QUERO O PLATINUM
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 mt-8">
      Compra segura · Acesso imediato após a inscrição · Suporte por WhatsApp
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
